- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses dynamic programming and algorithmic approach for monitoring. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes a new algorithm for monitoring. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper deals with monitoring of cyber-physical systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper discusses monitoring of running systems.
